Docker Images for Cyrus IMAP
============================

NOTE: The image will build against master by default.

Build it:

  $ docker build -t cyrus-imapd-3.0.el6 el6/

Run it:

  $ docker run -t -i cyrus-imapd-3.0.el6

Apply a differential to the build:

  $ docker run -e "DIFFERENTIAL=9" -t -i cyrus-imapd-3.0.el6

IMPORTANT: Only use the **number**

Check out a specific commit:

  $ docker run -e "COMMIT=<id>" -t -i cyrus-imapd-3.0.el6

Do both:

  $ docker run -e "DIFFERENTIAL=9" -e "COMMIT=<id>" -t -i cyrus-imapd-3.0.el6

